Richard Mdluli and co-accused Mthembeni Mthunzi are accused of kidnapping, assault and intimidation of Oupa Ramogibe who was married to Mdluli's former lover Tshidi Buthelezi. JOHANNESBURG – Judgment in the former Crime Intelligence boss Richard Mdluli’s 1999 kidnapping case is currently being delivered in the Gauteng High Court in Johannesburg. Mdluli and co-accused Mthembeni Mthunzi are accused of kidnapping, assault and intimidation of Oupa Ramogibe who was married to Mdluli's former lover Tshidi Buthelezi. WATCH LIVE: Judgment in the Richard Mdluli case 